div.font:
05-9_decisions_selector_settings.R
For each setting:
1) filter_expr (hard constraints)
2) target_col + n_per_target (coverage)
3) ranking:
• rank_mode=lex (rank_cols) OR
• rank_mode=mcda (mcda_score)
4) d_min_m (spacing via thinning)
5) point-on-surface for candidate points
Outputs: per-setting segments + points (tmp gpkg)
